Warren isn't doing well answering, but I get what she's saying. Bernie is better since he admits to the tax increase, but it goes to show how bad  the other candidates are imo. Of course we're going to raise taxes, no one is under any dumbass illusion that we're not. That you have to ask just proves how disingenuous you're trying to be about it.

&#x200B;

And we shouldn't be afraid to say we're gonna raise taxes to pay for healthcare regardless.
